          "steps": [
            "Diketahui: $v_0 = 20 \\text{ m/s}$, $a = 2 \\text{ m/s}^2$, $t = 5 \\text{ s}$",
            "Gunakan rumus: $s = v_0 t + \\frac{1}{2}at^2$",
            "$s = 20(5) + \\frac{1}{2}(2)(5)^2$",
            "$s = 100 + \\frac{1}{2}(2)(25)$",
            "$s = 100 + 25 = 125 \\text{ m}$"
          ],
